Shugaban Kasar Indiya zai halarta bude wani gini a wani yanki da aka yi tuhuma
Shugaban Kasar Indiya, Narendra Modi, zai halarci wani taron fara gina wata masallaci na Musulunci a yankin Arewacin Indiya inda wata masallaci ta 16th karni ta rushe ta hannun masu karfi na Musulmi a shekarar 1992, bayan da kungiyar da take kula da aikin gina masallacin ta sanar da hakan.
An gudanar da wannan taro a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, wata rana da masu shirya taron suka ce ta da alama mai kyau ga Musulmi amma kuma wata rana ce da ta nuna shekara daya bayan da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta Kasar Indiya ta karyata ikon kula da kanta da aka baiwa ɗayan ɗayan yankunan da Musulmi suka fi yawa, Jammu da Kashmir.
An bayyana alamomin ba zai iya gani ba ga masu goyon bayan da kuma masu kada kai ga Modi na Hindu nationalist Bharatiya Janata Party, ko BJP, wanda ya hada da alkawarin da ya yi na kashe makomar Kashmir ta musamman da kuma gina wata masallaci ga Ubangiji Hindu Ram inda masallacin Mughal-era ya kasance, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh da masu bauta suka yi imani da cewa shi ne asalin Ram.
Saboda cutar Korona ta ci gaba da yaduwa a Indiya, wanda ya bayar da tarihin kashi na uku a duniya, za a yada shirin a talabijin gwamnati kuma za a iya karbar masu halartar da kallon shirin, daga cikin kungiyar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko Kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, wata kungiya mai kishin Hindu da ke hada da BJP.
Spokesperson na kungiyar, Vinod Bansal, ya ce a cikin sanarwar da aka fitar a Asabar, za a yi amfani da gidan sanyi a matsayin "wata babbar makoma da za ta yi haske ta yadda za a samu zaman lafiya a tsakanin al'umma, hadin gwiwa da kuma tashi da jinin Hindutva," ko hanyar rayuwa ta Musulunci.
Aik shekara da ta wuce an warware matsalar da ta tsakanin su game da wurin bayan nasarar zaben BJP da ta yi nasara.
A watan Nuwamba, Kotun Mai Girma ta yanke hukunci a favor na gidauniyar al'umma, inda ta ce za a ba musulmi petisiyoyi goma sha biyar a wani wuri mai kyau.
Masu karfi na musulmi sun yi kokarin gina masallaci a kan wani gida da aka gina a gaban gari mai tarihi na Ayodya da masu karfi na Hindu suka yi ta kokarin yin haka da shekaru.
A watan Disamba 1992, bayan an rushe masallacin, ya haifar da zanga-zangar al'umma wadda ta kai ga mutuwar kimanin dubu biyu, mafi yawan su Musulmi ne.
Yayin da karar rufe gini ta ci gaba da ji a wata kotu mai dacewa.
