Yogi Adityanath, shugaban kasar Uttar Pradesh da kuma wani malamin addinin Hindu, ya nema Ayodhya ya yi wata sallah mai dorewa da tsarkakewa, kuma ya nema duk masallatai a cikin birnin su yi amfani da hasken ruwa kafin ziyarar Modi, wata rahotanni ta Press Trust of India ta bayyana.
