Masu aikin kare hakkinan sun samu nasara a wuta na Lassen County
Jami'an tsaron wuta suna samun nasara a kan wuta biyu da suka wuta fiye da 30,000 murabba'in a Lassen County, a arewacin Sacramento.
Jirgin mai kyau, wanda ya fara a kudancin Adin, an kama shi da 40% yayin da yake ci gaba da kashe gidajen mutane da ranches da kuma ayyuka na noma, ayyuka na kayan haihuwa da kuma ayyuka na kayan yanayi, ofishin Cal Fire sun ce a cikin sabon bayani ranar Asabar.
Bayan yana wuta makonni hudu, wuta ya ci yammacin 21,000, ya kashe gidajen bakwai da ya aika ma'aikatan wuta biyu asibiti.
Jiya da safe, masu yaki da wuta sun amfana da yanayin da ya yi sauƙi don gina kuma inganta layuka na kula.
Amma zafin gashi da karancin ruwan sama an sa ran za su yi tasiri har zuwa Asabar.
A kudu daga yammacin Susanville, wani wuta mai yawa da aka sani da Hog Fire ya gubar da gidaje biyu kuma ya cinye makiya kusan 10,000.
Jiya ta sauya yayin da masu aikin kare wutar lantarki suka yi aiki don tsabtace kuma inganta layukan karewa, bisa ga Ma'aikatar Kaliforniya ta Kare Wutar Lantarki da Kula da Wuta.
A ranar Asabar da safe, an kama 45% kuma ya yi wuta na shida kwanaki.
A cikin zafin rana, da yanayin zafi ya kai 90 digiri a yankin Susanville, yankunan da suka yi kumburi suna cikin riskar da za su fara haskaka.
Yayin da wasu masu zama suke aikata zuwa gidajensu, wasu yankuna a cikin duka yankunan wuta suna cikin umarnin kulle.
Biyu 'yan gaggawa da suka ji rauni a cikin wuta mai kyau sun fita daga asibiti.
Hausa: Algeria: Mutuwar Mahmoud Guemama - Algeria Ta Rasa Wani Dan'uwa, Wanda Ya Yi Aiki Tare Da Gaskiya, In Ji Shugaban Tebboune.
Aljir - Shugaban Kasa, Abdelmadjid Tebboune, ya aika sakonin takaici ga 'yan majalisar jama'ar kasa (APN), Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wanda ya rasu Alhamis, inda ya ce Aljirya "ta rasa jinin kasancewa da al'umma da kasa."
Yau Algeria ta rasa, ta yin rashi da mutuwar Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wani yan kishin kasa da al'umma da kuma kasa, wani mutum wanda bai taba yin wani sauyi ba kuma tabbacin sa ya kasance mai karfi daga lokacin da ya fara daukar makamai tare da 'yan Mujahedeen 'yan uwansa har zuwa lokacin da ya yi rashi a yau wannan ranar da muka kawo karshenmu ga Allah, Shugaban Tebboune ya rubuta cikin sakon ta'aziyyarsa.
"Mahmoud Guemama, Allah ya jikan sa, ya kasance daga cikin wata tsohuwar shekara ta masu yakin neman al'umma da suka yi wa kasar su rai, wannan ya kara da shugaban kasa,"
An mutu da ya rasu ya yi rayuwarsa don sakin Algeria daga cin zarafin kolonialism din makaho, ta shiga cikin kungiyar yakin neman zaman lafiya a shekarar 1960 a yankin Tahart na wurin tarihi na wilaya VI.
Shugaban da ya gabata ya san da dukkaninmu saboda tabbacin da ya nuna na yaki da kuma alfahari da ya yi na kafa hanyar da za ta sa Algeria ta zama mai arziki da kuma mai hadin kai, in ji Shugaban Tebboune.
A cikin kudancin mafi gabas, late Mahmoud Guemama yana da kyakkyawan suna a matsayin wanda ya yi wa kulawa, yana shiga tsakanin 'yan'uwa a cikin kasar da ke da yanayi idan an kunna wuta ta yi wa juna kuskure, ''in ji shugaban a cikin saƙonsa.
"Dukkan wadannan dabi'u da kima sun samar da late Mahmoud Guemama girmamawa da kuma aminci daga mutane Tamanrasset wadanda suka zaba shi don su raba su a cikin Majalisar Mutane ta Kasa (APN) a cikin yanayi da yawa, lokacin da ya kasance babban sakataren kuma mai kare muhimman abubuwan yankin da burin mutanen yankin, kuma ma wakilin kuma magatakardan dukkan Algerians," ya rubuta Shugaban Kasa.
Babu kalmarin tausayi da zai iya yin kyautata ga mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, amininsa, ba zai isa ba.
Yana barinmu yau a lokacin da Aljeriya take bukata shi," in ji shugaban.
Ina addu'a ga Ubangiji Mai Girma ya kare mutumin da ya rasu da RahamarSa ta Musamman, ya karbi shi cikin AljannarSa mai girma tare da shuhadar da masu aiki da kyau.
Na kuma ina addu'a ga Allah ya ba iyalinsa da masoya nasa jin dadi da kwanciyar hankali... babu iko ko karfi sai daga Allah," Shugaban Kasa ya kammala.
Seattle: Wuta da Magunguna a Matsayin Dubban Suna Tafiya Ta Hanyar Birnin
Bayan da yawan tashin hankali tsakanin masu yin zanga-zangar da hukumomin federal a Portland, Ore., an hada kai da yawan jama'a kusan dubu biyu a Seattle a Asabar, suka yi tafiya ta hanyar tituna da kuma yin tashin hankali da 'yan sanda.
Jami'an 'yan sanda uku sun ji rauni, ciki har da wanda aka ajiye a asibiti da rauni a kafafunsa da aka yi ta amfani da wuta, kuma har zuwa yamma, an kama 16 masu yin zanga-zangar, kamar yadda jami'an 'yan sanda suka ce.
Suna daukar alamomi kamar "Feds Tafi Gida" da kuma yin kirari na "Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya," yan tawaye sun tsaya a wurin da za a gina asibiti na yara da suka shiga laifin kuma suka yi wuta a cikin gidajen da ke nan.
Wasu kwandoni da aka kashe a kasuwanni da ke kusa.
Sojojin 'yan sanda sun taka rawar gani a yankin Capitol Hill, suna aiwatar da makamai na haske da mai kamshi kafin su fara daukar mutane cikin tsare.
Bipasha Mukherjee, 52, daga Kirkland, Wash., ta ce ta yi tserewa a tituna tun daga watan Mayu kuma ta ce ta yi tsoro sosai da ganin hanyoyin da sojojin 'yan sanda suke amfani da su.
Ms. Mukherjee, wadda ta zo daga Indiya da shekaru goma sha takwas da suka wuce, ta ce, "Wannan ba shi ne kasar da na yi ziyara ba."
Yana da kamar muna sauri kuwa muna zama wata kasar fashi da kuma wata kasar sojoji.
Michaud Savage daga Seattle ya ce taron neman hankali ya nufa ga ma'aikatan gwamnati da kuma aiwatar da ma'aikatan federal da suka yi watsi da taron neman hankali da ya yi tsawo a Portland.
Mr. Savage ya ce hanyoyin da aka yi amfani da su na kare doka a Portland, wadanda suka hada da amfani da mai kwacewa da kuma makamai na kare jama'a, suna da kariya kuma ba daidai ba ne.
Mr. Savage ya ce, "Yana da matukar wahala a cikin yanayi mai tsanani," yayin da ya tsabtace idanunsa da mai tsami da kuma yana kula da rauni a kafadarsa daga mai haske mai haske.
Mutuwar George Floyd a cikin hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a May ya sanya yankin ya yi karaya, wadanda suka kai miliyoyin mutane zuwa tituna a yankunan da dama, amma wadannan taron sun yi kasa a yankunan da yawa.
Seattle da Portland dai sun ga yin nuna-nuna da zama da yawa.
A wuraren da ke Seattle sun yi kokarin ɗaukar wasu ƙananan hanyoyin yankin Capitol Hill, kuma sun yi ƙaddamar da ƙasa mai ƙarfi.
Bayan wani tashin hankali na rikicin da ya sanya 'yan sanda suka kwace yankin, muhawara ta yi kasa.
Portland, a wani lokaci, ya ci gaba da yin protesto, tare da wasu daga cikin mafi girma protesto a yankuna na tsaro a birnin.
Bayan shugaban Trump ya bayar da umurnin kula da alamomin da kayayyakin majalisar dokoki, hukumar tsaron gida ta aika takaitattun tawagaggun zuwa birnin, wanda ya fara wani tsari na rikice-rikice da ya haifar da masu yin zanga-zangar da suka ji rauni, binciken jakadancin mai binciken, da kira daga jagororin yankin don a saki makamai na federal.
Jama'a masu yin bacin ran a cikin wannan birni sun karu sosai, kuma ayyukan nuna bacin ran a nan suna ci gaba.
Wannan mako, masu mulki na tarayya sun aika wani taktikal tawagar zuwa Seattle, kuma masu yin nuni sun bayyana wannan ci gaba a matsayin daya daga cikin dalilai da suka sanya a ranar Asabar a yi nuni.
Yayin da taron kuka a Portland ya tsaya a babban birnin, taron ranar Asabar ya yi tafiya a yankunan da ke gabas da babban birnin, inda kotun tarayya ta birnin ke.
Virginia Beach ta kwace tsayayyen makamin Konfedera
Birnin Virginia Beach, Va. -- Birnin Virginia Beach ya cire alamomin Konfedera na shekaru 115 daga wuraren yada labarai a ranar Asabar, da karancin biyu da suka gabata bayan kotun birnin ta yanke shawarar yin haka baki ɗaya.
A yau Asabar, jaridu suka bayyana cewa, aikin yi sun kwace babban alamar da ta kai 27-foot (8.2-meter) a ranar.
An aikata a 1905 kuma ya tsaya a waje na gidan kotun ta tsohon County Princess Anne, a wannan wuri da aka yi siyarwa ta bayi a baya.
