Aikin gaggawa na duniya don samar da magunguna masu amfani wajen magance cutar Covid-19 yana fuskantar matsala saboda jami'an binciken na Amurka suna gwaje-gwajen magunguna a hanyar "da ba ta da tsari ba, da ba ta da tsari ba," shugaban kungiyar da ke jagorantar shirin kasar Birtaniya ya yi wa sanarwa.
Gwamnatin Birtaniya ta yi gwajin karewa, wanda ya shafi 12,000 masu ciwon cuta a yankunan asibitoci da dama a Birtaniya, ya nuna wata magani mai amfani da za a yi amfani da shi wajen magance cutar, kuma ya bayyana wasu biyu - wadanda a baya an yi tunanin za su zama masu taimakawa rayuwa - a matsayin abubuwa da ba su da amfani.
