Bethe Correia, mai karfi mai karfi daga Brazil, ita ce mai tsohon UFC amma ta yi kuskure na amfani da kanta a kan mai karewa Pannie Kianzad, kuma ta yi kuskure ta tuni baya akan rana a cikin yarjejeniyar su akan Fight Island, kuma ta sami taga a sakamakon haka.
A karshe na farkon stanza na musayar su a kan undercard a Abu Dhabi, 37-shekara Correia ta yi kuskure ta gane 10-second warning a matsayin karshe na rana, ta kai hannunta zuwa ga Kianzad kafin ta juya baya zuwa ga corner nata.
Jirgin mai karewa daga Sweden ta yi amfani da rashin jin dadi, ta yi taga da hannunta dama kafin ta bi da wani tsari na kararraki wanda ya sa Correia a kasan gidansu.
A lokacin da ya bayyana a cikin wani matsala, sai Brazilian ya dakatar da wannan tashin hankali kafin kammala kwanan ya kira, yana kuma dawo da Kianzad.
Me ya faru a nan? Oh Allah, an ji karar yan kulawa na ESPN+ suna furta.
Ya kasance kawai ɗaya daga cikin dare mai cike da tashin hankali ga tsohon takarar mai suna Correia, wacce ta fadi zuwa ƙarar jarrabawa ta musamman wanda ya zama ta ta uku a cikin tafiye-tafiye ta ta hudu a cikin ɗakin octagon, kuma ya bar ta da rikodin 11-5, tare da ɗaya daga cikin jarrabawa.
Ga Kianzad, wadda aka haifa a Iran, mai shekara 28, wannan ya zama nasarar ta biyu bayan nasararta a kan Jessica-Rose Clark a UFC Fight Night a Moscow a watan Nuwamba.
Kianzad yanzu 13-5 baki daya kuma 2-1 a cikin UFC, yayin da mace da aka sani da 'Banzai' take nufin canja jerin 135lbs.
