Oh! Media ta samar da kudin da aka yi a farkon wannan shekara don tabbatar da tsaro na kudi yayin da cutar pandemiya ta fara kara tsoro ga masu sayar da tallace-tallace.
An ruwaito cewa kamfanonin suna tattaunawa yadda za su rage yawan raguwar da suka samu ta hanyar rage kudin shiga ga wuraren da suke aiki ko ta hanyar cire ko rage kudin tabbacin kudin da aka sanya lokacin da aka yi wannan siyasa.
Wasu daga cikin manyan masu tallata billboard sun tabbatar da cewa za su samu kashi 85 cikin 100 na kudaden da suka yi tunanin za su samu a matsayin kudin shiga.
Wasu kundayen yana da kudade da suka yarda su rage tabbacin mafi karancin idan yawan mutane a wani yanki ya rage da wata yarjejeniya, amma ba a san ko wannan yarjejeniya ta shiga cikin kowane daga cikin kundayen da billboard masu sayarwa suka yi da masu mallakar gidajensu ba.
A lokaci guda, kamfanonin suna bayar da rabon kuɗi mai yawa ga masu yada labarai don ɗaukar wuraren da suka rage a kan layukan gado da kuma baiwa su mafi yawan kudi mai amfani.
Kudaden da aka samu daga kafofin watsa labarai a cikin Sydney CBD da kananan birane da suka sanya hudu zuwa shida da adireshin suna fama da wahala wajen cika dukkanin wuraren da aka samu.
Amma wasu shafuka - kamar babban billboard na oOh! media 40 x 10 metre a filin jirgin sama na Sydney - suna da sabon tsarin.
Oh! Media ta kiɗa yin magana, amma a taron Macquarie Australia a watan Mayu, ta bayyana cewa za ta samu kudin kashe kudin gidaje na fiye da miliyan 20.
JC Decaux ta ki yarda da magana.
Asabar da jiragen sama da kuma hanyoyin sadarwa na jama'a suna daga cikin ayyukan da suka fi karfin kamfanonin billboard.
Bayan Rahoton Harkokin Waje na Association na 2019, kudin daga hanyoyin jirgin sama - ciki har da filayen jiragen sama - ya kai dala miliyan 169.4 yayin da kudin daga abin hawa da kuma waje na motocin bas da tram ya kai dala miliyan 266.5.
JC Decaux yana da ayyuka tare da Sydney Airport, Yarra Trams, Perth Airport da Sydney Buses. oOh! Media yana da billboard a cikin yankuna kamar Qantas lounges, waje Sydney airport, Adelaide Airport, Darwin Airport da cikin stashen jiragen ruwa a Sydney da Melbourne.
A lokacin pandemiyar, an yi aikin neman takardun Melbourne Airport da Sydney Trains, amma ba a yi wani shawarar rahoto ba.
Melbourne shi ne karbar karbar jirgin sama ta biyu a Australia da kafin cutar coronavirus ta kasance mai kimanin miliyoyin dala kowace shekara.
A cikin sakamakon shekara-shekara a Fabrairu, oOh! Media ta ce ta samar da $65.9 miliyan daga rukunin 'fly' nata, wanda ya fi yawa daga kudaden da ta samu daga Filin Jirgin Sama na Sydney.
Kudaden da aka samu daga 'tafiya', wanda aka hada shi da ayyukan layin jirgin kasa da kayan aikin wuraren zama da Adshel ta mallaka kafin a sayar da shi ga oOh!, ya kai dala 234.8 miliyan.
JC Decaux Australia ta samu kudin shiga daga ayyukan jirgin sama na 2018 na $37.7 miliyan, bisa bayanin da ta yi wa Australian Securities and Investment Commission a cikin sakamakon fina-finan 2018.
Amma dukkanin lambobin za su yi kadan sosai wannan shekara.
Bayanai daga Standard Media Index, wanda ya bayar da bayanin kudin biyar daga cikin hudu mafi girma ad agency groups, sun ce cinikin nuna adireshin waje ya yi kasa da 68 cikin 100 a watan Yuni.
A karshe, sakamakon watan Yuni sun nuna cewa kudin digital sun karu da 37 cikin 100, yayin da radio na birni ya karu da 48 cikin 100.
Talabijin na Metropolitani ya ragu da 34 cikin 100 a watan Yuni, kudin jaridu ya ragu da 49 cikin 100, kuma kudin mujallu ya ragu da 66 cikin 100.
