Jamie Vardy ya amince da rashin samun damar shiga gasar Champions League, amma ya ce Leicester City sun cimma burin su na shiga gasar Turai a farkon shekara.
Foxes sun sami biyu a watan Disamba kuma uku lokacin da kwallon kafa ta sake fara bayan tsaro, amma suka dauki kawai hudu daga cikin biyar wasanninsu don kammala na uku a cikin Premier League.
Za a sami nasara a kan Manchester United a ranar karshe zai tabbatar da samun matsayin hudu, amma tawagar Brendan Rodgers ta fuskanci rauni na 2-0, wanda Vardy ya ce shi ne mafi tsana a cikin hakan.
