Hannah Smith, shugabar Ice Scotland, ta bayyana kofar a matsayin wani "da yawan lura da shi" ɓangare na tarihin masana'antar Scotland.
Ta ce: "Muna sani cewa an yi masa suna a duniya baki daya kuma yana da muhimmanci cewa a nan gaba za a fara aikin gyara shi."
