Daga bisa ga masu sana, an karrama masu ziyarar bankin da suka yi, an kuma ba su shawarar su yi imani da aikin gwajin korona.
Da farko, wani mataimakin jami'in kantin wanda ke fama da wasu cututtuka, ya mutu saboda cutar COVID-19.
An bayyana yanayin da suka dace bayan an yi wani taro na likita a bankin a yanzu, an ce an bayyana hakan daga ofishin masu ruwa da tsaki.
