Pogba, daga gare shi, yana jin dadi a kungiyar kuma ya samu farin ciki sakamakon zuwan Bruno Fernandes.
An karbo daga Portugal ya zama wani abu mai ban mamaki a Old Trafford, kuma zuwansa ya baiwa Pogba damar yin wasa a matsayin wani mai karfi a tsakiyar tsakiya, wanda ya kara inganta yanayinsa.
